# JVM heap settings.
#
# Set the minimum (-Xms) and maximum (-Xmx) heap to the same value to avoid
# stop-the-world GC pauses while the heap resizes. Keep it at most 50% of system
# memory and below ~32 GB, so the JVM can use compressed object pointers.
-Xms{{ opensearch__heap }}
-Xmx{{ opensearch__heap }}
